data.description: Welcome to your own slice of paradise in this stunning country setting! Nestled on a sprawling wooded lot spanning just over 8 acres, this property offers the perfect blend of tranquility and adventure.  With 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this home provides ample space for comfortable living and entertaining. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a seamless flow for everyday living.  For outdoor enthusiasts, this property is an absolute dream come true. With just over 8 acres of land at your disposal, you'll have plenty of room to roam and explore. Whether you're an avid hunter or simply enjoy observing wildlife, this property offers endless opportunities to connect with nature.  Imagine waking up to the soothing sounds of nature and sipping your morning coffee, taking in the serene beauty of your own backyard.  In addition to these features, this property also offers the convenience of an RV hook up and clean-out. Whether you're hosting guests or looking for a place to park your own RV, you'll have everything you need right at your fingertips.  Located in a peaceful and secluded area, yet still within easy reach of modern conveniences, this property truly offers the best of both worlds. Don't miss your chance to own this remarkable country retreat. Schedule your private showing today and start living the life you've always dreamed of!
